First Niagara Bank Reviews & Info

First Niagara continues to stand out by delivering results for their shareholders, outperforming the industry and peer banks on key measures, believing in their customers and their ideas, and giving back to the communities where they do business. Their product portfolio may be their competitive advantage. But what really sets them apart is the people who've chosen to work here. If you're looking for a financial partner, First Niagara is a great place to do business. If you're looking to build your career, it's a great place to do that, too....see more
We strive to be first in what matters to our customers.  Helping you pay less, earn more, protect smarter and borrow wisely. As a wholly owned subsidiary, with billions in assets and deposits, thousands of employees and hundreds of branches across four states, we’ve built a trusted name by helping our customers, our employees and our communities. With specialized expertise across many facets of today’s financial world, we can help you thrive personally and professionally.
Other Names Used: Abraham Lincoln Federal Savings Association, Abraham Lincoln Federal Savings Bank, Albion Federal Savings and Loan Association, Amsterdam Federal Bank, Cargill Bank of Connecticut, Catskill Savings Bank, Cayuga Bank, Chicopee Co-operative Bank, Citizens Bank and Trust Company, Cohoes Savings Bank
