Find the Right Account








Traditional Accounts







Fifth Third Essential Checking










Fifth Third Essential Checking






Get all the essentials of a checking account and multiple ways to avoid a monthly service charge. 


Monthly service charges waived with any of the following:

A combined monthly average balance of $1,500 across your deposit and investment accounts1*
Spend of at least $500 per month on a Fifth Third credit card2
Any existing Fifth Third personal mortgage, auto loan or line of credit with an outstanding balance3

Otherwise, service charge is $11 per month (reduced to $8 per month with monthly direct deposits totaling $500 or more).4  



Apply Now

More Details













Fifth Third Enhanced Checking










Fifth Third Enhanced Checking






Earn interest on your checking account and get enhanced discounts and benefits. 


Monthly service charges waived with any of the following:

A combined total balance of at least $20,000 across your deposit and investment accounts one time per month5*
Monthly direct deposits totaling $5,000 or more4

Otherwise, it's $20 per month.  



Apply Now

More Details













Fifth Third Preferred Checking










Fifth Third Preferred Checking






Join this exclusive program to earn higher interest on your checking account and get preferred discounts, benefits and services.


No monthly service charge if you:

Achieve a combined total balance of at least $100,000 across your deposit and investment accounts one time per month6

Otherwise, it's $25 per month. 



Apply Now

More Details








Specialized Accounts







Student Banking










Student Banking






This personal checking account receives the same great benefits as Fifth Third Essential Checking, but with the monthly service charge waived for high school and college students age 16 and up.7 


Accounts opened by a minor (under age 18) require a parent or guardian to be a joint owner of the account and must be opened in the branch. No monthly service fee and no minimum balance requirements.




Apply Now

More Details













Fifth Third Enhanced Checking










Fifth Third Enhanced Checking






For military families, including active duty, retired, reserve/guard and veterans. Also includes commissioned officers of the Public Health Service and the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration.


 


Military Banking includes a Fifth Third Essential Checking account with all monthly service charges waived (saving $11 per month) with either:

$500 in monthly direct deposits4
A combined monthly average balance of $1,500 across your deposit and investment accounts1
Spend of at least $500 per month on a Fifth Third credit card2
Any existing Fifth Third personal mortgage, auto loan or line of credit with an outstanding balance3

 
  


If another option works better for you, you can choose any other Fifth Third Checking Account and get a $5 discount on the monthly service charge.8 



Apply Now

More Details













Fifth Third Express Checking










Fifth Third Express Checking






A new simple way to manage your funds. Fifth Third Express Banking gives you immediate access to your money and the convenience and security of a banking relationship.



Apply Now

More Details













